{
  "title": "Trident Robotics 4296",
  "about": {
    "heading": "About Us",
    "content": "<p>We are <strong>Trident Robotics Team 4296</strong>, a student-led high school robotics team dedicated to designing, building, and competing with innovative robots. Our mission is to spark curiosity, foster collaboration, and push the boundaries of technology through hands-on engineering experiences.</p><p>Founded in 2012, our team has grown into a community where students gain real-world skills in <em>design, mechanical engineering, electrical systems, and programming</em>. We don\u2019t just build robots\u2014we build future engineers, problem-solvers, and leaders.</p><p>Every season, our team comes together with one goal: to turn imagination into innovation and prove that when teamwork meets technology, the possibilities are endless.</p>"
  },
